cs.IR, cs.HC, cs.DL, cs.DB, cs.CL. 

The paper discusses a system for organizing and navigating web pages using collaborative tagging and hierarchical structures. This falls under the domain of information retrieval (cs.IR) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The system also leverages machine learning techniques such as deep learning (cs.DL) and database management (cs.DB) to improve the navigational capabilities. Additionally, natural language processing (cs.CL) is used to semantically navigate the pages.
